media:group.media:description:
#shorts ¡"Que no falte ninguno" era otro eslogan que pensé! Es importante que vaya la mayor cantidad de personas, espero que asistan 🇨🇱

The Chilean national plebiscite will be held in Chile on 4 September 2022 in order to determine whether the public agrees with the text of a new Political Constitution of the Republic 🗳️
